==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Decimalize
<hw>Dec"i*mal*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to convert
the dominant units of measure (e.g. of currency) to a decimal-based
system; to reduce to a decimal system; <as>as, to <ex>decimalize</ex>
the currency</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Dec`i*mal*i*za"tion</wf>
<pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Decimally</ent>⟦br⟧
